File: Electricity switched off City Power JOHANNESBURG - Power utility Eskom announced load reduction in Gauteng will be taking place on Tuesday afternoon. The load reduction will be implemented between 5 pm and 10 pm. READ: Eskom CEO justifies upcoming tariff increases Areas in Soweto and the Vaal will be affected, including Dobsonville, Sharpville, Orange Farm, Powerville and Vereeniging. Eskom Load Reduction Notice
